metadata.description: NounsNationGDCF is a crowdfunding initiative to raise money to fund the development of a video game called NounsNation. NounsNation is an interactive web3 game with unique characters and gameplay. The NounsNation dev team is going to release assets and scenes from a prototype game as NFTs to raise money and show the community its progress. The supply of the NounsNationGDCF collection is limited to 1,000 NFTs. NFTs will be released in small batches and sold via auction bimonthly.
